reviewText: I chose this rating because it was so far my least favorite of all Laurel and Hardy films.  It is the only Laurel and Hardy film I have seen so far where the boys do not play a major role. Because they do not appear until the middle of the film I thought at first perhaps I bought the wrong tape.
like i said im a man of few words but i think it was a all right movie and it was funny take my advise and check out this movieif your a laurel and hardy fan like me.
